Happy Father’s Day to the #BadaamRaj @rajubhatia62 

Kyu sale kam karva rahe ho Dad? Let people eat more almonds! 

PS - in india we have a myth of eating just 5-6 almonds soaked overnight. But in a lot of research and studies done by the Almond Board of California @californiaalmonds suggest the perfect serving size as an ounce - 28 grams - or 22-24 almonds! 

Yes guys ! So I know you’re not going to soak more overnight, but you can snack on almonds throughout the day!!! 

Go for it ! Don’t hold yourself back, especially when you have the yummy almonds from @nuttygritties 

#Almonds #fathersday #healthysnacking #californiaalmonds
